    "description": "Omni Logistics India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Distribution Manager at our Ahmedabad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Omni Logistics India:\nOmni Logistics India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Omni Logistics India!",
